                        </div>
                        <div class="p-8">
                            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3 group-hover:text-green-600 transition-colors">Spotify</h3>
                            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Leading music streaming service with personalized discovery and seamless cross-platform experience for 350M+ users.</p>
                            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-6">
                                <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-green-100 text-green-700 rounded-full text-xs font-medium">Personalization</span>
